title: Book of Life and Death
summary: Book of Life and Death For high school student Grant Lee, luck was like a clean pair of socks: never there when you need it the most. But when he finds a mysterious book that can tell the future, he’s sure it’s all about to change. For starters, he saves the life of Hannah Lin, the prettiest girl in school! But things take a turn for the worse when he gets swept up by powerful forces vying for control of Willow City. In order to survive and win Hannah’s heart, he’s going to need a lot more than luck. Chao Ji Da Zhu Bu The Master of Fate The Super Book of Death 超级大主簿
